These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, fisherman, librarian, manager
1. the fisherman is in an odd position##4
2. the manager is between the analyst and the fisherman##2
3. the manager is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Job   | analyst | manager | fisherman | librarian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill, ritmeester, game
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Cigar   | dunhill | bluemaster | game | ritmeester |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, october, july, january
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
2. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in october##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Birthday   | may | january | july | october |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
