.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, sailing, swimming
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2       |     3      |  4   |
| Sport   | sailing | biathlon | swimming | baseball |

