.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, zombie, drama, disaster
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
4. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | disaster | superhero | zombie |

