2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |    3     |    4     |
| Hobby   | woodworking | card-games | camping | sudoku |

