.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, metal, rock, hip-hop
1. the fan of metal is the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
3. the fan of rock is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | hip-hop | metal | electronic |

